   - If no operator is named, use ROUTING.md to infer the lane from the task shape:
     - Execution, coordination, follow-up → Claudia
     - Technical direction, architecture → Anton
     - Implementation delivery, engineering → Jonah
     - Design, UI/UX → Vera
